raw.name: #1 Mistletoe
raw.bio: Heyo! I'm #1 Mistletoe. All you need to know about me is I hate chocolate with a passion. Some people say I'm the Peter Griffin of the group. This will be an amewsing friendship.

raw.name: #1st eva Santa.
raw.bio: Ciao! I'm #1st eva Santa.. My friends describe me as raunchy and annoying. When I'm not summoning ghosts, I'm volunteering at the local kitten rescue shelter! I hope you like kitten around as much as I do!
